<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Trial ended — Risk2Safe</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink:#0B1220; --surface:#F5F3EE; --green:#1B5E4F; --green-bright:#2C8A73;
    --amber:#C97A2C; --grey:#8B93A1; --display:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;
    --body:'Inter',sans-serif; --mono:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
  }
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
  body {
    background: var(--ink); color: var(--surface); font-family: var(--body);
    min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 32px 20px;
  }
  .panel {
    width: 100%; max-width: 520px; background: var(--surface); color: var(--ink);
    border-radius: 6px; padding: 44px 40px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .panel::before {
    content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--amber), #B0492F);
  }
  .icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; margin: 0 auto 20px; }
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--amber); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  h1 { font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.6rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  p.sub { font-size: 0.94rem; color: #5a6478; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-direction: column; }
  a.btn {
    display: block; padding: 13px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none;
    font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.92rem;
  }
  a.btn-primary { background: var(--green); color: #fff; }
  a.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--green-bright); }
  a.btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: var(--ink); border: 1px solid #d8d4c8; }
  .fine-print { margin-top: 22px; font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--grey); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="panel">
  <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="#C97A2C" stroke-width="2">
    <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="18"/>
    <path d="M24 14 V24 L31 29"/>
  </svg>
  <div class="eyebrow">Trial Period Ended</div>
  <h1>Your 7-day trial has wrapped up</h1>
  <p class="sub">
    Thanks for spending the week with the Risk2Safe toolkit. To keep using HAZOP Studio,
    RA Studio, BowTie Studio, and the rest of the suite, get in touch and we'll set you
    up with a plan that fits your team's size and the way you work.
  </p>
  <div class="cta-row">
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:contact@risk2safe.com?subject=Risk2Safe%20—%20Continued%20Access%20Enquiry">Contact us about continued access</a>
    <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://risk2safe.com">Back to risk2safe.com</a>
  </div>
  <p class="fine-print">We'll follow up directly using the details from your trial signup.</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
